sentences: Born in Bloomfield, Iowa, United States, Reno appeared at the Grand Ole Opry in the 1960s, and played with Waylon Jennings and Dolly Parton.
He named as the Country Music Association's Disc Jockey of the Year in 1978.
Reno died of brain cancer on November 1, 2008 in Florence, Kentucky.
